{"tid":303092,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Intern 銀行 vs 大型代理商，點簡好？","createTime":"2017-06-30T01:43:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-30T02:49:38.000Z","uid":97904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"08045bb0a05fcfd9510b2444f5baf4fc57d18ded","tid":303092,"uid":97904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T01:43:00.000Z","msg":"兩個intern 既position 性質都唔一樣。<br />\n第時grad 左想做marketing, 過多幾年希望可以拎個MBA, 但自己本身讀緊social science 科.<br />\n但銀行就係做文職多，做下filing, 整下ppt 咁，係投訴部入面做。<br />\n大型代理商係間美國公司，幾出名下，但做既野係人力資源部門入面。<br />\n諗左好耐，都唔知邊條路會較適合我想行個條路. 各有好同壞.<br />\n有無巴絲打可以比到意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8419e4466f0fe0d44d9c177777730c5919749f78","tid":303092,"uid":97904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T01:50:37.000Z","msg":"Pish <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ba93a51eba0649186b7b7b16e60ac9028f28789","tid":303092,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T01:52:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e6fef034370d363fad07da575562057cdcc3bd13","tid":303092,"uid":21423,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T01:52:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9be2274c49eeb1fac80f1126d4a973d8b2faecdb","tid":303092,"uid":97904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T02:10:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試著說「俾」，不要說「比」。</blockquote><br />\n又係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae79b982e67848564c2e3c3d3925fbbd7ddf4ca2","tid":303092,"uid":97904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T02:49:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoh